---
import BaseLayout from '../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Listening" description="What I've been listening to">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col">
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center">What am I listening to?</h1>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="row mt-4">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 mb-5">
        <div class="flex justify-end">
          <iframe data-testid="embed-iframe-song" style="border-radius:12px" 
                src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/6gqTgtJ3aBDrWE9wrCe7L6?utm_source=generator&theme=0" 
                width="100%" height="152" class="spotify-widget"
                allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" 
                loading="lazy">
          </iframe>
        </div>       

        <div class="p-3 text-xs text-left my-auto">
          <h2 class="font-semibold">Currently obsessed with...</h2>
          <p>I'm currently obsessed with <em>The Song of Orpheus</em> by Ruari O'Connor.</p>
          <p>This song draws from Greek mythology and is a beautiful piece of music; it is sung in greek and I <i>cannot</i> stop listening to it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 mt-5 border rounded-lg">
        <div class="p-3 text-xs text-right my-auto">
          <h2 class="font-semibold">If you need a laugh...</h2>
          <p>Check out <em>Toni and Ryan</em>. I've been an avid listener for years, and they never cease to make me laugh, a fantastic podcast especially when you need an uplift.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex justify-start">
          <iframe data-testid="embed-iframe-podcast" style="border-radius:12px" 
                  src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/show/5OzkclFjD6iAjtAuo7aIYt?utm_source=generator&theme=0" 
                  width="100%" height="152" class="spotify-widget"
                  allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" 
                  loading="lazy">
          </iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
